ow they work. Named arguments can indeed be in any order. However, once named arguments are used, it seems that any positional arguments that follow must also be named. It's important to clarify that to avoid confusion in setting up method calls. Okay, I’ll make sure to remember this nuance when discussing Scala 3 further!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0dae7cd8514718c70169fb5b14bd6c819091a9baa8cf7794b2\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-1sspwbwFuq9RjqCl8T6Sm1QznUedq1zW5PACn4WyVl5jIo_tMHQBzS2cnrPvH0AZHP0kXWWtriWUs6_y8X63LgbhE31TbsqGtl1NJKdJX3LBBKvceWmx76-MniShEkK8xm_wU7gHuzyenAsJgapr7wAOmd-IN41PHY8_hjRzzI8EYs1pXNYBXhX78yWlcrM0uy21UnABzOUa2eddif4YWUKiBMYu_29ue_j2PY6MMRO6jTbQx1OoRs2aB6u1-docwdH44cXlp6wLmYMouDBvQKGK2_uXefh94sYq9miWMGcR2d7rmZXYlnwPEq75k96ZorkoL_6jCFPoAL0lrkTXAs2CxgwXi9WPwT8lPuE0_u6pPWDBGKvBjuTmVwCncM0MPx3JJTVbSh5rSkoKUF3mXQkyTer5nO7VGIpiHygM33ElSwNzagZApa6XG7BbxqljVZXAvhXpSp2_APXqYupt_aRKdqvkdmuYVur4PTJs76GCsETEBZV0D4nTe1eMLS33XIGMuxcTAFpf45TR5jHV3aCl1P8PMYZrzlWnO-a_GVD_Yl5n-YDLLqm8PrmMOGFdoPbntD9ODhqkWYkb8z7QLOchldmE_YwfrJopI997PIm8GSUrKm7lc0vvVEhtphUhaIdJ6I6ZFMzsfAyT0zz5yKP2ZY66KdLeLC6dTyMaNUXIL_0d_XpetZHeynoqu8FlBTT-buy1yil7hspCRtOWI-TDbc_NGszb88WptMWDIL9op1H66fjkLRB5nUw3ckWWsi2FTjYwBi3qsgBbIdK82hsIKYqN7y8LulcKEPr1WPV4UTY7df6eFcTt6Y6O57ulckxD87l4vZ6vnXtUKeQCfU1cXBrcqkmG5ZOEvmO0XAhMEtjQkAPTYMkcYHBinIt9JSsqXJXS4k3Ew5-wffHJJ9ncmBU7YZ7MYCEw07Qf49UzblBNdrKgFyTWBdQVVtM9HBjp5rDh3iJVpG0XZlpeTyUHjIB37u015ZNmdJITm6Q_HqMZvRxS3V36giwb697C0_nZAEbH6_P9HdrkHR_oN0FJAyfHDf8_uOzrJqqvQ0UEQe8O7nORtDhy5TCJz_J0N-G4FanGuKI9eGAsMkmFiORLYjDiOcCflFBKHCzjTvZxKq9XJAjeQvotyzgfEab_-ktCUXVHNGFGPKl5VQTXDmgmiaVL2mKUGIZc7cm29kSBEv96QNQnZ1fdVwWxuiNO9UIALNLc_Oad9KzG-j3kG_m5NjEz2Dp-y6XZ5l7VCBBzdCNa_6Gpd11g70CY071IFYapNlqSzhwV7YPyzZVMch0lqTp-xC5lh7uwW9lN_Ou3DraQNUApzzANp6OjVrimnHMPo2rJaLQUr0XQzl92ls_BFVpOG_P_Q9CsFcSr9H9f7T96knsMlqQrB8Sue5avrEJMguEn3F9OHsXdXOXubHfle85PiTQR7iwG1W16-KruxDInAevZBQ4ZyRXIuc9Fcpp_wbKLwSGOyCaMyYsfUcqfgEKDbRPNVfVt6N45vnUPbBSRxF8AY2QeW